{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"785546570b","title":"毛泽东给毛逸民的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"82ccacbc0c","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":8,"articleId":"785546570b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0895a48680","type":"title","text":"毛泽东给毛逸民的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"6c4564e7b3","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"1a8f6d4b58","type":"appellation","text":"逸民同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"f604d2b771","type":"paragraph","text":"一月三日来信收到，感谢你的好意，感谢你详细地将乡里情形告诉我。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"64991cc606","type":"paragraph","text":"乡里贫苦人民生活困难，烈士家属更加困难，暂时只好忍耐一点，待土地改革后就可能好一些了，那时人民政府也可能给人民以一些帮助，例如贷款等，人民就可以逐步改善自己的生活。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"3bff8d4d79","type":"paragraph","text":"烈属的照顾是全国范围内的事，全国有几百万户烈属，都要照顾，自未便单独地特殊地照顾少数地方。但最困难的人民，当地人民政府在减租时土改时及青黄不接的岁月，应当尽可能给以照顾。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"455e6a33c3","type":"paragraph","text":"你在乡里做工作，很好，可以常常来信，告我以乡中情形。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"805264aad0","type":"paragraph","text":"请你替我问候乡里的同志们，希望大家努力和进步。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"7e4446f246","type":"paragraph","text":"此复，顺祝","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"99de88c9ca","type":"appellation","text":"健康！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"},{"id":"54bd785e70","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛  泽  东一九五O年五月八日","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b"}],"page":{"id":"43e204ecb2","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"785546570b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}